sentences: In 1947, he joined the Communist Party of China.
After 1949, he was appointed the Vice President of the China Conservatory of Music and the head of the Chinese Opera House.
In 1978, a partial collection of his songs was published.
A festival dedicated to Ma Ke, called the China Xuzhou Ma Ke Art Festival, was held in Xuzhou in June 2004.
